
> Si vas a desplegar la app (Heroku, Render, Railway...), reemplaza `localhost:8080` por la URL pública del despliegue.

---

## 5) (Opcional pero recomendable) Añadir CI con GitHub Actions
Crea archivo: `.github/workflows/ci.yml` con este contenido para compilar y ejecutar tests:

```yaml
name: CI - build & test

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main ]
  pull_request:
    branches: [ main ]

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Set up JDK 17
        uses: actions/setup-java@v4
        with:
          java-version: '17'
          distribution: 'temurin'
      - name: Cache Maven packages
        uses: actions/cache@v4
        with:
          path: ~/.m2/repository
          key: ${{ runner.os }}-maven-${{ hashFiles('**/pom.xml') }}
          restore-keys: |
            ${{ runner.os }}-maven-
      - name: Build with Maven
        run: mvn -B -DskipTests=false clean package
